-## Constraints
+## Tips
 
-- All implementation goes in `src/index.ts`
-- No external runtime dependencies (dev dependencies are provided)
-- Must export `TaskQueue` as a named export
-- Tests use `vi.useFakeTimers()` for timing-sensitive tests
